The head of the Russian contact group for an intra-Libian settlement at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation and the State Duma, the assistant head of the Chechen Republic, Lev Degov, told us what the objectives of Moscow in the region are and on whom he is betting.
The contact group on Libya, which you are chairing, is almost unknown.
Let's say the contact group on Ukraine -- everyone knows about it.
And here is a cloak of mystery.
What exactly do you do, what are your goals?
The contact group was established at the initiative of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation and the State Duma.
