You, as we understand it, are in all the Libyan regions, and you probably imagine the sentiments of local elites and field commanders.
Do you think it will be possible to implement the cease-fire agreements, the elections reached at the end of July in Paris by Khalifa Haftar and Faiz Saraj?
Or again, as has been the case many times in the past, the agreements will be shattered, the fighting will resume, the parties will try to take power alone?
