The election is to take place, as was the case at a meeting between Saraj and Haftara.
If the elections are held and the legitimate power is finally elected (and none of the parties now has such a status), the question of lifting the arms embargo can be raised in the UN Council.
To raise this issue now is pointless and dangerous, it will only lead to an escalation of the conflict.
