I don't want to go into this detail.
Then we'll put the question differently.
How many of the Muslim militants in Libya are the Libyans themselves?
There are virtually no Libyans among them, not more than 5 per cent.
The rest are incoming.
Can Moscow hold intra-Libish talks like Paris?
There are plans.
We are engaged in intensive negotiations with the Libyans, several delegations from Libya have already visited Moscow, and have indicated their readiness to go to Moscow or Grozny again.
